snippet.title: Bamerang - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Bamerang is OUT NOW!
Smack your friends with Boomerangs when Bamerang launches April 22nd on the Nintendo Switch and Steam!
Get it on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1236490/Bamerang/
Get it on the Switch: https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/bamerang-switch/

Music and SFX by Lucien Guy Montandon
